        size - amount of neurons this Layer (will) contain(s)
        withBias - whether or not a bias-neuron should be included
        activationFunction - activation function to be applied to the weighted sum in the process of feedforwarding
        errorFunction - error function that is used to measure the discrepancy between the desired output and the actual output
